  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nThe method `verify_proof_of_possession` has been changed to `validate_proof_of_possession`.\r\nThe new method has already been written in eth2/types/beacon_state.rs but has not been implemented.\r\n\r\nThis also requires eth2/utils/bls/lib.rs create_proof_of_possession to be updated to reflect the the changes in validation.\r\n\r\n## Present Behaviour\r\n\r\nCurrently it operates functionally based on a previous spec version\r\n\r\n## Expected Behaviour\r\n\r\nSee Eth2.0 specs for more detail.\r\n\r\n## Steps to resolve\r\n\r\nImplement `validate_proof_of_possession`\r\nModify `create_proof_of_possession`\r\n",
